{"page":7,"source":"d:/ITSupport/knowledge_base/IT Helpdesk FAQ.pdf","chroma:document":"5\n2. HOW TO LOG INTO OKTA\nSTEP 4 \nSometimes, if Okta detects unusual \nactivity or a potential threat, it may ask \nyou to complete a number challenge to \nsecure your account.\nSTEP 5\nOnce logged in your dashboard will contain shortcuts to \napplications you already have access to or can request access \nt